&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;209&quot; data-end=&quot;236&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;213&quot; data-end=&quot;234&quot;&gt;Account Executive (Onsite SF)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;237&quot; data-end=&quot;550&quot;&gt;As an Account Executive at Pump, you’ll play a key role in driving our growth by building strong relationships and helping customers understand the real impact of our technology. This is an exciting opportunity to join a fast-growing team, contribute to our product, and help shape our company culture and values.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;557&quot; data-end=&quot;579&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;561&quot; data-end=&quot;579&quot;&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;580&quot; data-end=&quot;1208&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;580&quot; data-end=&quot;696&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;582&quot; data-end=&quot;696&quot;&gt;Partner closely with our tech, design, and leadership teams to develop solutions that align with customer needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;697&quot; data-end=&quot;850&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;699&quot; data-end=&quot;850&quot;&gt;Engage with prospective customers to understand their business challenges and clearly explain how Pump can streamline operations and save them money.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;851&quot; data-end=&quot;951&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;853&quot; data-end=&quot;951&quot;&gt;Effectively communicate the value of our platform to both technical and non-technical audiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;952&quot; data-end=&quot;1059&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;954&quot; data-end=&quot;1059&quot;&gt;Stay up-to-date on our product roadmap and ensure client solutions are aligned with future development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1060&quot; data-end=&quot;1208&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1062&quot; data-end=&quot;1208&quot;&gt;Build and maintain strong relationships with key customers, acting as the bridge between clients and internal teams to ensure a smooth experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1215&quot; data-end=&quot;1245&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1219&quot; data-end=&quot;1245&quot;&gt;What We&#39;re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1246&quot; data-end=&quot;1771&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1246&quot; data-end=&quot;1341&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1248&quot; data-end=&quot;1341&quot;&gt;3-5 years of relevant experience in a sales, business development, or customer-facing role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1342&quot; data-end=&quot;1403&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1344&quot; data-end=&quot;1403&quot;&gt;Excellent communication skills — both verbal and written.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1404&quot; data-end=&quot;1475&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1406&quot; data-end=&quot;1475&quot;&gt;Ability to thrive in a fast-paced, constantly evolving environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1476&quot; data-end=&quot;1573&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1478&quot; data-end=&quot;1573&quot;&gt;Strong cross-functional collaboration skills — especially with engineering and product teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1574&quot; data-end=&quot;1682&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1576&quot; data-end=&quot;1682&quot;&gt;A self-starter mentality with grit, hustle, and a desire to make a big impact at an early-stage startup.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1683&quot; data-end=&quot;1771&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1685&quot; data-end=&quot;1771&quot;&gt;Competitive, athlete mindset and a drive to change your life through this opportunity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1778&quot; data-end=&quot;1794&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1782&quot; data-end=&quot;1794&quot;&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&l

&lt;p&gt;As an Account Executive at Pump, you’ll play a key role in our growth by owning the full sales cycle—from sourcing and qualifying leads to closing deals and building long-term client relationships. You’ll work closely with our CEO, product team, and fellow early sales hires to shape our go-to-market strategy and sales culture from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a career-defining opportunity for a resourceful, high-performing seller who wants to help scale a YC-backed startup tackling a massive $500B+ market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Responsibilities -&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the full sales process: outbound prospecting, discovery, demos, proposals, and contract closure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate daily with the CEO to shape pipeline strategy and execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage with inbound and outbound leads to identify pain points and communicate Pump’s value proposition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain strong, trusted relationships with decision-makers and technical stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with the product team to tailor solutions to client needs and provide customer feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistently meet and exceed monthly, quarterly, and annual revenue goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as an internal champion for customer success and retention&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain up-to-date and accurate pipeline activity in HubSpot&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Qualifications -&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2–5 years of experience in B2B SaaS or cloud infrastructure sales, ideally with a proven track record of closing deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of the sales cycle from prospecting to closing, with clear examples of quota achievement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication and presentation skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience engaging technical buyers, especially in cloud or DevOps-related conversations, is a big plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with CRM software like HubSpot, Salesforce, or similar tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly self-motivated and comfortable operating in a fast-paced, startup environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work cross-functionally with product and engineering to communicate customer needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A customer-first mindset and strong relationship-building skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Business, Marketing, or a related field preferred—but not required if experience is strong&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Benefits -&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salary aligned with local market standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performance-based bonuses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company equity options&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive healthcare coverage for you&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;13 days PTO + 1 week company shut down December 24—January 1&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quarterly team retreats and offsites&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible work arrangements, including hybrid/remote options where applicable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Compensation&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;₹2,000,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;₹3,000,000 INR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Pump.co&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gartner predicts that cloud spend will be over $2T/yr by 2030, making it the fastest-growing expense for tech companies. Managing it well demands constant engineering effort—time that could be spent building your product.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At &lt;strong&gt;Pump&lt;/strong&gt;, we&#39;re building the fastest way to save ~60% on cloud costs. Our AI-powered platform not only automates savings but also leverages the power of group buying for even deeper discounts. Backed by &lt;strong&gt;Y Combinator&lt;/strong&gt;, we’re on a mission to transform cloud cost optimization through AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our founding team includes experienced entrepreneurs with prior exits, and our culture is fast-paced, collaborative, and flat in structure. If you’re excited about shipping real impact and joining a team at an early, career-defining stage—we’d love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills:&lt;/strong&gt; Python, FastAPI, PostgreSQL, AWS, Docker, Kubernetes (nice to have), LLM/AI (bonus)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Backend Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;, you’ll contribute directly to the core of our product and infrastructure. This role is ideal for someone looking to grow within a strong engineering team while delivering meaningful work that touches real customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll collaborate closely with engineers, designers, and founders—working across the stack to build, improve, and scale our platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are 5 days a week in office. No remote work will be considered.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, build, and maintain backend services that power the Pump platform&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with the team to define and scope new product features&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to a strong engineering culture by participating in code reviews and continuous improvement&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help extend our internal tools, dev workflows, and CI/CD pipelines&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure system reliability, performance, and maintainability&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate across functions to solve real customer problems with intuitive engineering solutions&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3–15 years of professional backend engineering experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;5 days a week in office&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in &lt;strong&gt;Python&lt;/strong&gt; and familiarity with &lt;strong&gt;FastAPI&lt;/strong&gt; or similar frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with &lt;strong&gt;SQL databases&lt;/strong&gt;—we use &lt;strong&gt;PostgreSQL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort working in a cloud environment (AWS preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with containerization and orchestration tools like &lt;strong&gt;Docker&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Kubernetes&lt;/strong&gt; (nice to have)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excitement about early-stage startups and the ability to thrive in fast-moving environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear communication and collaborative instincts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with &lt;strong&gt;cloud billing/cost tooling&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interest in or exposure to &lt;strong&gt;LLMs or AI integrations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with &lt;strong&gt;NoSQL databases&lt;/strong&gt; like Dynamo

&lt;p data-start=&quot;144&quot; data-end=&quot;484&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;144&quot; data-end=&quot;162&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;144&quot; data-end=&quot;484&quot;&gt;We’re hiring a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;180&quot; data-end=&quot;199&quot;&gt;Brand Designer&lt;/strong&gt; to design and produce high-quality &lt;strong data-start=&quot;235&quot; data-end=&quot;263&quot;&gt;visual and motion assets&lt;/strong&gt; for web, email, social, events, and sales enablement. This is a high-impact, creative-first role where you’ll collaborate across marketing, product, and leadership teams to define how the world sees and experiences Pump.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;486&quot; data-end=&quot;717&quot;&gt;While this role spans core brand and visual design, we&#39;re actively looking for someone with strong motion design capabilities. You’ll be a key creative partner in telling compelling stories through both static and animated content.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;719&quot; data-end=&quot;741&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;719&quot; data-end=&quot;739&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;742&quot; data-end=&quot;1456&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;742&quot; data-end=&quot;841&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;744&quot; data-end=&quot;841&quot;&gt;Design and produce high-quality visual and motion assets for digital, brand, and campaign needs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;842&quot; data-end=&quot;988&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;844&quot; data-end=&quot;988&quot;&gt;Create custom graphics, illustrations, infographics, and motion/animated content to support product launches, GTM, and internal communications&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;989&quot; data-end=&quot;1188&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;991&quot; data-end=&quot;1188&quot;&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally on brand evolution, content strategy, and integrated marketing campaigns, partnering closely with marketing teams to drive audience engagement and demand generation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1189&quot; data-end=&quot;1277&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1191&quot; data-end=&quot;1277&quot;&gt;Own and evolve Pump’s design system to ensure visual consistency across all channels&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1278&quot; data-end=&quot;1372&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1280&quot; data-end=&quot;1372&quot;&gt;Support executive, investor, and sales presentations with creative design and storytelling&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1373&quot; data-end=&quot;1456&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1375&quot; data-end=&quot;1456&quot;&gt;Contribute to overall creative strategy and participate in campaign brainstorms&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1458&quot; data-end=&quot;1487&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1458&quot; data-end=&quot;1485&quot;&gt;Required Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1488&quot; data-end=&quot;2091&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1488&quot; data-end=&quot;1595&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1490&quot; data-end=&quot;1595&quot;&gt;3–5 years of experience in visual or motion design, ideally at a fast-paced startup or B2B SaaS company&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1596&quot; data-end=&quot;1685&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1598&quot; data-end=&quot;1685&quot;&gt;A strong portfolio demonstrating both static and motion work across digital and brand&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1686&quot; data-end=&quot;1746&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1688&quot; data-end=&quot;1746&quot;&gt;Proficiency in Adobe After Effects and &lt;strong&gt;Framer (required)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1747&quot; data-end=&quot;1820&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1749&quot; data-end=&quot;1820&quot;&gt;Fluency in Adobe Creative Suite, Figma, and othe

&lt;p&gt;As a Business Development Representative, you&#39;ll be a key player in helping our company grow. Your role involves building relationships and explaining how our tech solutions can make a real difference. It&#39;s a chance to be part of a fast-growing team and contribute to both our product and company values.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Responsibilities -&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with our tech, design, and leadership teams to create solutions that match what our customers need.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Chat with potential customers, understand their business challenges, and explain how Pump can make their lives easier and save them money.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outbound through various channels including email, cold call, LinkedIn, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show why our tech is valuable, whether you&#39;re talking to tech experts or those new to it all.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand our product roadmap and make sure our solutions align with what our clients are looking for.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep strong ties with key customers. Be the bridge between customers and our teams to ensure everything runs smoothly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Qualifications -&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear communication skills: Speak and write clearly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This would be a fast-paced job. Things might change, and tech is always evolving.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work well with different teams. Communicate with engineering, product, and others to ensure customers are happy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Athlete mentality, a chip on the shoulder, and the desire to change your life through the startup.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Benefits -&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3061&quot; data-end=&quot;3094&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3063&quot; data-end=&quot;3094&quot;&gt;Comprehensive healthcare and dental coverage for you&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3095&quot; data-end=&quot;3110&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3097&quot; data-end=&quot;3110&quot;&gt;401(k) plan&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3111&quot; data-end=&quot;3154&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3113&quot; data-end=&quot;3154&quot;&gt;Generous PTO: 13 accrued days, plus company shutdown December 24—January 1st&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3155&quot; data-end=&quot;3199&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3157&quot; data-end=&quot;3199&quot;&gt;Free lunch &amp;amp; dinner at the office&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3200&quot; data-end=&quot;3232&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3202&quot; data-end=&quot;3232&quot;&gt;Annual company-paid retreats&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3233&quot; data-end=&quot;3258&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3235&quot; data-end=&quot;3258&quot;&gt;Developmental bonuses: support for professional development opportunities tied to cloud and related fields&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3233&quot; data-end=&quot;3258&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3235&quot; data-end=&quot;3258&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;941&quot; data-end=&quot;958&quot;&gt;Compensation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;$110,000–$180,000 OTE + 2,500–5,000 stock options&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Compensation&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$110,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$180,000 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

