&lt;li&gt;Show why our tech is valuable, whether you&#39;re talking to tech experts or those new to it all.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand our product roadmap and make sure our solutions align with what our clients are looking for.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep strong ties with key customers. Be the bridge between customers and our teams to ensure everything runs smoothly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
