&lt;li data-start=&quot;1002&quot; data-end=&quot;1092&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1004&quot; data-end=&quot;1092&quot;&gt;Partner with the sales team to facilitate client onboardings and architecture reviews.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
