&lt;p data-start=&quot;1095&quot; data-end=&quot;1195&quot;&gt;Assist clients pre- and post-sale with onboarding and troubleshooting issues on the Pump platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1196&quot; data-end=&quot;1300&quot;&gt;
