&lt;p&gt;You will play a critical role in building our platform, driving the technical direction of our company. This is a hands-on position that will involve working on all things infrastructure, and collaborating with other engineers, designers, and founders. A great opportunity for someone to create a lasting impact not only on the primary product but also on the company&#39;s values and vision, given our early stage - we hope Pump would be that career defining opportunity for all of us!&lt;/p&gt;
